File list and information:
------------------------------

_item.rhtml
A partial that displays one post item, without details. This is used when
listing posts (such as on the main page or in monthly archives).

_item_detailed.rhtml
A partial that displays one post item with details. Use this for things like
permalink pages, where you might want comments shown, et cetera.

show.rhtml
Displays one post item, using the _item_detailed.rhtml partial (this is a
permalink view).